snippet.title: Rose & Locket Alpha Demo Runthrough
snippet.description:
This is a recording of the newest alpha demo of Rose & Locket, which is currently available on Itchio: https://whistlingwizard.itch.io/rose-locket
and Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/Roseandlocket/473988

Rose & Locket is an action-adventure journey set in the Wild West. Follow Rose as she ventures into the Underworld to free the trapped spirit of her daughter.

Cinematic moments accompanied by sprawling landscapes and intense action combat.

Enter into the Underwest and take up the once-forgotten skills of the gunslinger.

Made by Whistling Wizard
Follow our work here:

https://twitter.com/WWGAMINGNZ
https://www.instagram.com/whistlingwizardnz/
